{"tid":1645041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家到底係想煲底見新彊見?","createTime":"2019-10-10T18:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T02:26:35.000Z","uid":47659,"like":95,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"35457b63a7917c5e1c0d25ce45703811cc5a2fbf","tid":1645041,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"10月6日至10月7日 以下句子一直蔓延 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&quot;<strong>等美國通過法案啦 忍下手啦 唔差在呢幾日啦, 我地比律師朋友做野啦 休息啦..............&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結果呢? 呢幾日發生咩事啊?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">看更因為拒絕比暴徒進入住所被捕<br />\n暴徒街上亂咁拉 有無口罩都拉<br />\n黨鐵日日宵禁 屈示威者<br />\n浮屍又出現 未成年既都有</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n你班休息撚係咪又想<span style=\"color: red;\">等等等</span>?<br />\n等到<span style=\"color: red;\">新彊嶺建成全港200萬人一齊送入去集中營先行動好無?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪再信咩野仲有幾多日通法案忍下手<br />\n咩野律師朋友做緊野忍下手<br />\n咩野民意逆轉外媒唔鐘意暴力忍下手<br />\n...........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場不是不合作運動, 呢場不是公民抗命咁簡單<br />\n呢場係一場革命, 係一場戰爭, 雙方都將所有賭本儘押<br />\n根本係無任何空間可以喘息 你估暴徒一方就算無活動, 又唔係晚晚開OT搜證拉人咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估林鄭開行會無傾過動用更多緊急法咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地<span style=\"color: red;\">只要人,<strong>一齊趕絕休息撚 付諸行動 自己香港要自己救<br />\n<br />\n不要將抗爭外判 不要愧對義士 不要到香港變成新彊才後悔</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1ERLcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1ERLcz.jpg&h=1ea16afc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fa8db4b2e66446b605441b39c82bd9a8d760658","tid":1645041,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:05:18.000Z","msg":"10月6日至10月7日 以下句子一直蔓延 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&quot;<strong>等美國通過法案啦 忍下手啦 唔差在呢幾日啦, 我地比律師朋友做野啦 休息啦..............&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結果呢? 呢幾日發生咩事啊?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">看更因為拒絕比暴徒進入住所被捕<br />\n暴徒街上亂咁拉 有無口罩都拉<br />\n黨鐵日日宵禁 屈示威者<br />\n浮屍又出現 未成年既都有</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n你班休息撚係咪又想<span style=\"color: red;\">等等等</span>?<br />\n等到<span style=\"color: red;\">新彊嶺建成全港200萬人一齊送入去集中營先行動好無?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪再信咩野仲有幾多日通法案忍下手<br />\n咩野律師朋友做緊野忍下手<br />\n咩野民意逆轉外媒唔鐘意暴力忍下手<br />\n...........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場不是不合作運動, 呢場不是公民抗命咁簡單<br />\n呢場係一場革命, 係一場戰爭, 雙方都將所有賭本儘押<br />\n根本係無任何空間可以喘息 你估暴徒一方就算無活動, 又唔係晚晚開OT搜證拉人咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gi