啦..............&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結果呢? 呢幾日發生咩事啊?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">看更因為拒絕比暴徒進入住所被捕<br />\n暴徒街上亂咁拉 有無口罩都拉<br />\n黨鐵日日宵禁 屈示威者<br />\n浮屍又出現 未成年既都有</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n因為我地休息左兩日, <strong>呢幾日其實我地已經輸到仆街</strong><br />\n你班休息撚係咪又想<span style=\"color: red;\">等等等</span>?<br />\n等到<span style=\"color: red;\">新彊嶺建成全港200萬人一齊送入去集中營先行動好無?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪再信咩野仲有幾多日通法案忍下手<br />\n咩野律師朋友做緊野忍下手<br />\n咩野民意逆轉外媒唔鐘意暴力忍下手<br />\n...........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場不是不合作運動, 呢場不是公民抗命咁簡單<br />\n呢場係一場革命, 係一場戰爭, 雙方都將所有賭本儘押<br />\n根本係無任何空間可以喘息 你估暴徒一方就算無活動, 又唔係晚晚開OT搜證拉人咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估林鄭開行會無傾過動用更多緊急法咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地<span style=\"color: red;\">只要人,<strong>一齊趕絕休息撚 付諸行動 自己香港要自己救<br />\n<br />\n不要將抗爭外判 不要愧對義士 不要到香港變成新彊才後悔</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1ERLcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1ERLcz.jpg&h=1ea16afc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"966f35c5250e689c4ac0bd7b703aecac33712b25","tid":1645041,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"453704b18a6df5f644f1dc0caccc262118f05506","tid":1645041,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"we win or we die"},{"pid":"26acc892253c1936b2a9cb36802cd31d7f523b9d","tid":1645041,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"推動BLIZZCON國際戰線要錢要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1647163/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1647163/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"38b6e856d67c764ed927496ab202135a9b4fa2a1","tid":1645041,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"推】"},{"pid":"fa4f4c6a904305325eb9ebae9c420452f1754ea7","tid":1645041,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:33:39.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e047ccbcf2e39f48ddb8dcaae66475200b45d3aa","tid":1645041,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"【遍地再開花】香港人報仇！星期日 14:00 十八區再開花<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644618</a><br />\n<br />\n星期日見呀屌你地 18區<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajKwiuU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg